strict regulations.

00:05:15.780 --> 00:05:19.980 align:middle line:90%


00:05:19.980 --> 00:05:22.680 align:middle line:84%
I think, due to the
safety of these controls,

00:05:22.680 --> 00:05:24.930 align:middle line:84%
milk is an excellent
