00:05:26.760 --> 00:05:31.513 align:middle line:90%


00:05:31.513 --> 00:05:33.978 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:05:33.978 --> 00:05:45.810 align:middle line:90%


00:05:45.810 --> 00:05:48.890 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:05:48.890 --> 00:05:51.820 align:middle line:84%
