an effect on our health.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:06.495 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:06:06.495 --> 00:06:09.400 align:middle line:90%


00:06:09.400 --> 00:06:11.290 align:middle line:84%
We have an appointment
with a specialist

00:06:11.290 --> 00:06:15.265 align:middle line:84%
for food intolerances, and meet
Dr. Maximilian Ledochowski.

00:06:15.265 --> 00:06:16.065 align:middle line:90%
In his surgery.

00:06:16.065 --> 00:06:21.740 align:middle line:90%


00:06:21.740 --> 00:06:23.020 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:06:23.020 --> 00:06:27.550 align:middle line:10%
>> Milk, as we know it today,
