00:08:34.980 --> 00:08:38.267 align:middle line:90%


00:08:38.267 --> 00:08:39.100 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:08:39.100 --> 00:08:40.690 align:middle line:90%
