00:11:57.622 --> 00:11:59.990 align:middle line:90%


00:11:59.990 --> 00:12:01.460 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING GERMAN]

00:12:01.460 --> 00:12:06.140 align:middle line:84%
>> One dairy cow produces around
28,000 liters in its lifetime--

00:12:06.140 --> 00:12:09.730 align:middle line:84%
