00:12:09.730 --> 00:12:17.730 align:middle line:90%


00:12:17.730 --> 00:12:21.150 align:middle line:84%
Conventionally speaking, we
are a little above average.

00:12:21.150 --> 00:12:23.910 align:middle line:84%
