Otherwise, it won't
produce much milk.

00:12:34.100 --> 00:12:35.507 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING GERMAN]

00:12:35.507 --> 00:12:36.914 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING GERMAN]

00:12:36.914 --> 00:12:38.790 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING GERMAN]

00:12:38.790 --> 00:12:40.440 align:middle line:90%
>> They're not agitated.

00:12:40.440 --> 00:12:43.200 align:middle line:84%
That's how you can see you're
doing everything right.

00:12:43.200 --> 00:12:44.140 align:middle line:90%
They're not nervous.

00:12:44.140 --> 00:12:46.070 align:middle line:84%
They're not kicking,
but standing calmly.

00:12:46.070 --> 00:12:48.570 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:12:48.570 --> 00:12:50.570 align:middle line:90%


00:12:50.570 --> 00:12:54.050 align:middle line:84%
>> The quality of the milk and
its makeup is determined by how

00:12:54.050 --> 00:12:55.400 align:middle line:90%
