00:15:21.970 --> 00:15:26.072 align:middle line:90%


00:15:26.072 --> 00:15:27.030 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:15:27.030 --> 00:15:28.580 align:middle line:90%
>> The cow has changed.

