What the cow eats is
important, as the feed

00:15:34.200 --> 00:15:37.500 align:middle line:10%
influences milk production.

00:15:37.500 --> 00:15:41.100 align:middle line:10%
The milk has fundamentally
changed, at the latest

00:15:41.100 --> 00:15:43.830 align:middle line:10%
since 1983 is shown in studies.

