>> If milk, then organic
milk, advises Dr. Rau.

00:16:19.940 --> 00:16:22.260 align:middle line:84%
But what is the difference
between organic milk

00:16:22.260 --> 00:16:23.430 align:middle line:90%
and conventional milk?

00:16:23.430 --> 00:16:25.406 align:middle line:90%
[BELLS RINGING]

00:16:25.406 --> 00:16:27.382 align:middle line:90%


