00:17:48.890 --> 00:17:50.914 align:middle line:90%
And that is eating grass.

00:17:50.914 --> 00:17:51.902 align:middle line:90%
[COWS MOOING]

00:17:51.902 --> 00:17:53.878 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:17:53.878 --> 00:17:55.360 align:middle line:90%


00:17:55.360 --> 00:17:59.330 align:middle line:84%
